非典时期的爱情。
Love in the SARS Period.
网上冲浪记事。
Surfing on the Internet.
文化。
Culture.
为了祖国下一代，戴上口罩谈恋爱。
Wear a mask to fall in love for the next generation.
。
.
2003年非典期间，汪涵在一档综艺节目中向搭档马可抛出了一个问题：“在两个人两情相悦的时候，如果情急之时会发生什么状况呢？”。
During SARS in 2003, Wang Han asked his partner Mark on a variety show, "What happens when two people are having a good time?"
还没等马可回答，汪涵就从手中亮出了一张照片，一对年轻情侣隔着口罩相拥亲吻。
Before Ma could answer, Wang Han flashed a picture of a young couple hugging and kissing through a mask.
汪涵用俏皮的湖南方言说道：“戴了口罩都忍不住。
"Wear masks," Wang said in a witty Hunan dialect.
”。
"
马可打断汪涵：“一个口罩有16层，两个口罩是32层，隔着32层怎么亲热？”。
Marco interrupted Wang Han: "A mask has 16 layers, two masks are 32 layers, how do you love each other across the 32 floors?"
汪涵当场开车：“我跟你讲，当两个人有感觉的时候，都是半个小时了，那口水都透过去了，这对人猛啦。
"I tell you, when two people have feelings, it's been half an hour, and all that saliva has gone through," Wang Han said.
”。
"
玩笑归玩笑，汪涵在最后还是用了一段七字口诀，向电视前的情侣们宣传了特殊时期的正确恋爱方式：青山绿水多可爱，漂亮女子人人爱，为了祖国下一代，戴上口罩谈恋爱。
You should write at least 120 words and you should base your composition on the outline (given in Chinese) below: You should write at least 120 words and base your composition on the outline given in Chinese below: 1.
。
.
“倾城之恋”。
The love of the city.
在历史长河的任何阶段，爱情都是人类所向往的一种情感，而在一些特定时期，这种情感就更加显得弥足珍贵。
In any stage of history, love is a kind of emotion that human beings yearn for, and in some specific period, this kind of emotion is even more precious.
。
.
非典期间，很多大学采取了封闭式管理，里面的人出不去，外面的人进不来。
During SARS, many universities adopted a closed management system in which people could not get out and people from outside could not get in.
伴随着消毒水的气味，恐慌情绪也弥漫在人群中。
With the smell of disinfectant, panic swept through the crowd.
病毒肆虐的日子里，校园爱情给很多人的心中带来了温暖的感觉。
In the days when the virus raged, campus love brought warm feelings to many people's hearts.
。
.
当时清华的门户网站开展了“喜欢清华的N个理由”征集活动，很多学生提起喜欢清华的理由时，都表示在那里找到了一份美丽的爱情。
When Tsinghua's Web portal launched the "N Reasons to Like Tsinghua," many students, citing their reasons for liking Tsinghua, said they had found a beautiful love there.
当学校封闭实行分餐制时，不同宿舍楼的学生分配到了不同食堂就餐，但校园情侣没有被食堂拆散，他们用饭盒把饭菜从食堂端出，两两一对出现在操场看台，宿舍门口，小树林的长凳。
When the school system was closed, students from different dormitory buildings were assigned to different canteens, but the campus couple was not separated by the canteen. They carried the food out of the cafeteria in a lunch box, and two or two pairs appeared on the grandstand, at the dorm door and on the bench in the woods.
。
.
每天定时集中对宿舍消毒，让喜欢宅在宿舍的学生走出了宿舍。
Regular daily focus on the dormitory disinfection, so that students like to stay in the dormitory out of the dormitory.
在令人提心吊胆的日子里，大家三五成群的坐在一起，开始互相了解，甚至成为恋人，有人将这浪漫的称为“倾城之恋”。
On scary days, people sit together in groups and start getting to know each other and even become lovers. Some people call this romantic "love of the city."
非典爆发五年后，红网采访了一位大学教授的爱情故事，这位教授说“没有非典她不会成为我太太”。
Five years after SARS broke out, Red Net interviewed a university professor who said she would not be my wife without SARS.
。
.
非典爆发时，教授与他太太还都是学生。
When SARS broke out, both the professor and his wife were students.
此前女方曾明确的拒绝过他，但非典疫情改变了这一切。
She had explicitly rejected him before, but the SARS epidemic changed all that.
当时她经常向他倾诉自己的紧张与害怕，而他则拿出一副很爷们的样子为她壮胆，托朋友从校外捎来好吃、好玩的给她解闷，炎热的夏天给她送去亚麻凉席。
She often confided her nervousness and fear to him, and he showed her a very manly look, entrusting friends with delicious and fun from outside the school to relieve her, hot summer sent her linen mat.
。
.
有同学因食物中毒被急救车拉走，他太太当时并不知道具体情况，发短信说自己十分紧张，这位教授回了一则至关重要的短信：“要是你隔离了，我陪你去。
His wife, unaware of the circumstances, sent a text message saying that she was very nervous. The professor replied with a crucial text message: "If you're quarantined, I'll go with you.
”。
"
2003年4月23日，北京街头一对情侣。
April 23, 2003, a couple on the streets of Beijing.
除了同校之间的爱情，封闭管理下，还有很多不在同一所学校的情侣。
In addition to coeducational love, under closed management, there are many couples who are not in the same school.
他们隔着冰冷的铁栅栏相拥，以此表达爱意和鼓励。
They hugged each other across the cold iron fence as a gesture of love and encouragement.
。
.
破损的爱。
Broken love.
压抑紧张的气氛下，并非所有爱情都是美好的。
Not all love is beautiful in a stressful atmosphere.
这些年有不少影视剧都将非典这段往事穿插其中，其中不乏青春题材的校园故事。
In recent years, many movies and TV dramas have interspersed with the story of SARS, including the campus story of youth.
。
.
2014年热播的《匆匆那年》描述了一段校园爱情故事。
"Scurry Year," a hit in 2014, describes a love story on campus.
故事的结尾或许有些狗血，男主陈寻出轨，女主方茴用自己身体报复与别人上床，最终堕胎。
At the end of the story, there may be some dog blood, the male master Chen Chin-cheated, female Fennel with his own body revenge with others, abortion.
非典此时已经爆发，街上的行人都戴上了口罩，而方茴也在非典疫情期间故意避开陈寻，从此消失。
SARS has now erupted, the streets of pedestrians wear masks, and anthranil during the SARS epidemic deliberately avoided Chen, since then disappeared.
。
.
很多原著读者和观众都不太能接受这个结局，觉得方茴为何要如此作践自己。
Many readers and viewers of the original works are not able to accept this outcome, the anthranil why to behave so badly.
但也有不同的看法，当时贴吧上有人发问，“骂方茴不理解方茴的孩子，你们大学里经历过非典吗？”。
But there are different views, then paste on someone asked, "anthranil does not understand the children of your university has experienced SARS?"
楼主在帖子中讲述了自己在非典时的校园见闻。
In his post, the landlord told me what he saw on campus when SARS happened.
他的一个好哥们上大学谈了一年多恋爱，结果在非典期间女生变心，与另外一个系的男生好上。
A good friend of his went to college to talk about love for more than a year, but during SARS, the girl changed her heart and fell in love with a boy from another department.
。
.
后来他的哥们去女生宿舍找她，希望女友能够回心转意，结果却被挖墙脚的男生叫人打了一顿。
Later his buddies went to the girls' dorm looking for her, hoping her girlfriend would change her mind, only to be beaten up by the diggers.
。
.
“我们系男生知道后，差点和那男的系发生几百人对几百人的群殴，是老师给压下来了。
"When we learned about it, we almost got into a brawl with that guy's department, where hundreds of people fought against hundreds of people.
非典时正好大二，真的觉得世界末日似的。
SARS just happened to be sophomore, really feel like the end of the world.
好多人表白了，许多分分合合。
A lot of people confessed, a lot of points fit together.
”。
"
2003年4月22日，一对戴口罩的情侣在北京火车站相拥。
On April 22, 2003, a pair of masked couples embraced at the Beijing railway station.
虚假的爱。
False love.
特殊时期会产生出大量贴合事件的报道，但其中总会伴随着一些人为制造的假新闻。
Special periods produce a great deal of coverage of events, but they are always accompanied by artificially created false news.
。
.
2003年5月7日，一张非典期间的爱情题材照片登上了报纸头版，画面中一对情侣穿着婚纱，戴着口罩，穿过马路去拍照。
On May 7, 2003, a picture of a SARS love story appeared on the front page of a couple in wedding dresses and masks crossing the street to take photos.
。
.
这张照片名叫《非典时期的爱情》，作者是邱焰，他曾获得过中国德艺双馨摄影记者称号，后来这张照片经过国内评审送到了荷赛奖参赛。
The photo, titled "Love in the SARS Period," was written by Qiu Yan, a former Chinese German photographer who was sent to the Hershey prize after a domestic review.
。
.
荷赛奖被认为是国际专业新闻摄影比赛中最具权威的赛事，邱焰的《非典时期的爱情》在2004年第47届荷赛奖被评为了日常生活新闻类三等奖。
The lotus prize is considered the most prestigious international professional journalism competition, and Qiu Yans love of the SARS period was named the third prize in the Daily Life News category at the 47th lotus prize in 2004.
。
.
获奖消息传到国内后，邱焰却因此惹上了麻烦。
When the award was announced to China, Qiu Yans got into trouble for it.
。
.
照片中的“新郎”陈英真实身份是男模，他称《非典时期的爱情》的人物和场景全都是人为制造出来的，摄影记者邱焰为了拍摄“非典”时期为背景的爱情题材照片，在一家婚纱店选中了陈英和另一位女模特帮忙。
The photo of the groom, Chen Ying, is a male model who claims that the characters and scenes of "Love in the SARS Period" were all artificially created. Photographer Qiu Yans chose Chen Ying and another female model to help him in a wedding shop for a picture of love against the backdrop of SARS.
。
.
陈英为了提高自己知名度，愿意接受拍摄，要求照片以模特身份登报，并且不作结婚新人报道，但最终登报时邱焰未能履约。
Chen, who was willing to be photographed, asked to model and not be reported as a newlyweds to raise her profile, eventually failed to comply.
一年后，获奖的消息传来，陈英将邱焰告上了法庭。
A year later, the award was announced and Chen Ying took Qiu Yue to court.
法庭上，他称照片是由邱焰亲自导演、一手策划，自己因这张严重失实的新闻照片导致他与女友关系破裂。
In court, he said the photo was directed and masterminded by Qiu Yans, and that his relationship with his girlfriend had broken down because of this grossly inaccurate news photograph.
。
.
但另一方面，陈英时隔一年、照片获奖才起诉，有人怀疑他是为了搏出位，模特和演艺圈为出位不惜炒作自己的例子当时也并不少见。
But Chen, on the other hand, was prosecuted only every year after the photo was awarded, and it was not uncommon for him to be suspected of playing for the throne, and models and acting circles to hype up their own examples.
而且起诉前不久，陈英还曾向邱焰索要10万元了结此事，但最终被邱焰以遭到敲诈为由向警方报警。
And shortly before the indictment, Chen Yin also asked Qiu Yin for $100, 000 to settle the matter, but was eventually called to police by Qiu Yans for extortion.
。
.
首次开庭后，邱焰面对媒体采访时，还一口咬定这张获奖照片并非摆拍。
After the first session of the court, Qiu Yans face the media interview, also insisted that this award-winning photo is not posed.
但随着4个月时间里的3次开庭，《非典时期的爱情》最终被判失实。
But with three court sessions in four months, Love in the SARS Period ended up being untrue.
。
.
法院在判决书中称：“图片新闻应当遵循新闻真实性原则，本案照片经原告同意，由第一被告邱焰拍摄并配发文字说明，次日，《武汉晚报》作为图片新闻予以发表，该文字说明没有直接反映‘街道口罩秀’营销活动，而是对照片反映事实的拔高处理。
"Photographic news should follow the principle of truthfulness of the news," the court said in a ruling. "The photos were taken by Qiu Yans, the first defendant, with the plaintiff's consent. The next day, Wuhan Evening News was published as a photo news item.
”。
"
陈英觉得这场审判总体是公正的，但对于“街道口罩秀”的说法有些不满，“根本不存在什么口罩秀的活动”。
Chen Ying felt the trial was generally fair, but complained about the "street mask show," saying "there is no such thing as a mask show."
。
.
这场官司让陈英拿到了三万元的精神赔偿，但他当时在电话里接受《今日早报》采访时并没有很高兴：“赔得太少。
Chen Ying received 30,000 yuan in compensation for his mental illness, but he wasn't happy about it in a telephone interview with the Morning Post.
对于邱焰曾说我敲诈，我和律师商议后准备另打官司讨回名誉，他这样做对我做生意的家人造成恶劣影响。
The fact that Qiu Yans said I was blackmailed and that I was going to take another lawsuit against him after consulting with my lawyer had a bad effect on my family in my business.
”。
"
热恋、分手、造假的爱情转眼过去了17年，曾经非典时期的爱情故事，变成了如今新冠时期的情人节。
Love, break-up, fake love passed 17 years ago, once SARS love story, has become the new crown of Valentine's Day.
。
.
今年的情人节如刚过去的春节一样冷清，商场和街头不再灯火通明。
Valentine's Day this year was as cold as the Spring Festival, with no lights on in the mall or on the street.
线上零售的热搜商品由往年的鲜花、巧克力，变成了口罩和酒精。
Online retailing of hot search products from flowers, chocolate, into masks and alcohol.
这次学生没有被困在学校，但却困在了家里，异地恋通过手机屏幕开始了漫长的云恋爱，等这场疫情结束，可能又将是另一种独特的爱情故事。
This time the students are not trapped in school, but trapped at home, long-distance love through the mobile phone screen began, and so the end of the epidemic may be another unique love story.
。
.
